{"type":"message","id":"6580ee8f","parentId":"b1e26309","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:16:25.104Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:85f4bcff-e1bf-408e-953a-f9ea83b5e0d7 task:85f4bcff-e1bf-408e-953a-f9ea83b5e0d7] 用户反馈小说审核后台登录时报错。\n\n请检查：\n\n1. 后台页面代码：\n   - `/var/www/novel/abyss/admin.html` - 查看登录逻辑\n   - 登录时调用的 API 端点是什么\n   - Token 是如何发送的\n\n2. API 服务端代码：\n   - `/root/.openclaw/workspace/novel-project/api/server-v2.js` - 查看认证逻辑\n   - ADMIN_TOKEN 的定义和验证方式\n   - 登录接口的实现\n\n3. Nginx 配置：\n   - `/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/` 中 kuroneko.chat 的配置\n   - `/novel/abyss/api/` 或 `/abyss/api/` 的代理配置是否正确\n   - 后端服务端口（应该是 3456）\n\n4. 检查后端服务状态：\n   - `systemctl status abyss-server` 或 `pm2 list`\n   - 服务是否在运行\n   - 查看最近的错误日志\n\n5. 如果发现问题，修复它。\n\n输出：\n- 具体的错误原因\n- 修复方案（如果需要修复）\n- 修复结果\nCurrent time: Friday, February 27th, 2026 — 3:16 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772176585102}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7b708ae","parentId":"6580ee8f","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:16:34.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户报告小说审核后台登录时报错。我需要系统地检查以下几个方面：\n\n1. 后台页面代码 - 查看登录逻辑\n2. API 服务端代码 - 查看认证逻辑\n3. Nginx 配置 - 查看代理配置\n4. 后端服务状态 - 检查服务是否运行\n\n让我逐步检查这些文件和配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来系统检查小说审核后台的登录问题。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ed7b986bc5f846feb21669aa","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/var/www/novel/abyss/admin.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ef11df92e72849e0a5afc56d","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/novel-project/api/server-v2.js"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0064210dbb264ecca93e0eb1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":331,"output":146,"cacheRead":32512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32989,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772176585103}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ae4d8b7","parentId":"d7b708ae","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:16:34.771Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ed7b986bc5f846feb21669aa","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>审查员后台 - 深渊代行者</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/abyss/static/style.css\">\n    <style>\n        .admin-container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .admin-header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .admin-header h1 {\n            margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n        }\n        \n        .admin-header p {\n            margin: 0;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n        \n        .stats-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n            gap: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .stat-card {\n            background: white;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        \n        .stat-card h3 {\n            margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #666;\n        }\n        \n        .stat-card .number {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #1a1a2e;\n        }\n        \n        .stat-card.pending .number {\n            color: #ff9800;\n        }\n        \n        .stat-card.accepted .number {\n            color: #4CAF50;\n        }\n        \n        .stat-card.rejected .number {\n            color: #f44336;\n        }\n        \n        .filters {\n            background: white;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 15px;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        \n        .filters label {\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        \n        .filters select {\n            padding: 8px 12px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        \n        .annotation-table-container {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        table {\n            width: 100%;\n            border-collapse: collapse;\n        }\n        \n        thead {\n            background: #f5f5f5;\n        }\n        \n        th, td {\n            padding: 15px;\n            text-align: left;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n        }\n        \n        th {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #666;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        \n        .paragraph-preview {\n            max-width: 200px;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            text-overflow: ellipsis;\n            color: #666;\n            font-size: 13px;\n        }\n        \n        .annotation-content-preview {\n            max-width: 250px;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        \n        .status-badge {\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding: 4px 12px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        \n        .status-badge.pending {\n            background: #fff3e0;\n            color: #ef6c00;\n        }\n        \n        .status-badge.accepted {\n            background: #e8f5e9;\n            color: #2e7d32;\n        }\n        \n        .status-badge.rejected {\n            background: #ffebee;\n            color: #c62828;\n        }\n        \n        .action-buttons {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 5px;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-accept, .btn-reject, .btn-reply, .btn-delete {\n            padding: 6px 12px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-accept {\n            background: #4CAF50;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-accept:hover {\n            background: #45a049;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-reject {\n            background: #f44336;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-reject:hover {\n            background: #da190b;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-reply {\n            background: #2196F3;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-reply:hover {\n            background: #0b7dda;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-delete {\n            background: #999;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-delete:hover {\n            background: #666;\n        }\n        \n        .modal {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            z-index: 2000;\n        }\n        \n        .modal-content {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            max-height: 80vh;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n        }\n        \n        .modal-header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        \n        .modal-header h3 {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        \n        .modal-body {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .form-group {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        \n        .form-group label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        \n        .form-group textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-family: inherit;\n        }\n        \n        .form-actions {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: flex-end;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-primary {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-secondary {\n            background: #f5f5f5;\n            color: #666;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        \n        .btn-close {\n            background: transparent;\n            border: none;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        \n        .empty-state {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            color: #999;\n        }\n        \n        .hidden {\n            display: none !important;\n        }\n        \n        .login-screen {\n            max-width: 400px;\n            margin: 100px auto;\n            padding: 40px;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        \n        .login-screen h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 登录界面 -->\n    <div id=\"login-screen\" class=\"login-screen\">\n        <h2>🔐 管理员登录</h2>\n        <form id=\"login-form\">\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <label for=\"admin-token\">管理员令牌</label>\n                <input type=\"password\" id=\"admin-token\" required\n                       placeholder=\"请输入管理员令牌\" style=\"width:100%; padding:10px; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:4px;\">\n            </div>\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-primary\" style=\"width:100%;\">登录</button>\n        </form>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- 管理界面 -->\n    <div id=\"admin-screen\" class=\"admin-container hidden\">\n        <div class=\"admin-header\">\n            <h1>📋 审查员后台</h1>\n            <p>深渊代行者批注管理系统</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- 统计卡片 -->\n        <div class=\"stats-grid\">\n            <div class=\"stat-card\">\n                <h3>总批注数</h3>\n                <div class=\"number\" id=\"total-count\">0</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card pending\">\n                <h3>待处理</h3>\n                <div class=\"number\" id=\"pending-count\">0</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card accepted\">\n                <h3>已采纳</h3>\n                <div class=\"number\" id=\"accepted-count\">0</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card rejected\">\n                <h3>已拒绝</h3>\n                <div class=\"number\" id=\"rejected-count\">0</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- 筛选器 -->\n        <div class=\"filters\">\n            <label>状态：</label>\n            <select id=\"status-filter\" onchange=\"loadAnnotations()\">\n                <option value=\"\">全部</option>\n                <option value=\"pending\" selected>待处理</option>\n                <option value=\"accepted\">已采纳</option>\n                <option value=\"rejected\">已拒绝</option>\n            </select>\n            \n            <label>章节：</label>\n            <select id=\"chapter-filter\" onchange=\"loadAnnotations()\">\n                <option value=\"\">全部章节</option>\n            </select>\n            \n            <button onclick=\"loadAnnotations()\" class=\"btn-primary\">刷新</button>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- 批注表格 -->\n        <div class=\"annotation-table-container\">\n            <table>\n                <thead>\n                    <tr>\n                        <th>章节</th>\n                        <th>原文</th>\n                        <th>批注内容</th>\n                        <th>类型</th>\n                        <th>作者</th>\n                        <th>状态</th>\n                        <th>时间</th>\n                        <th>操作</th>\n                    </tr>\n                </thead>\n                <tbody id=\"annotation-tbody\">\n                    <!-- 动态加载 -->\n                </tbody>\n            </table>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- 回复模态框 -->\n    <div id=\"reply-modal\" class=\"modal hidden\">\n        <div class=\"modal-content\">\n            <div class=\"modal-header\">\n                <h3>回复批注</h3>\n                <button onclick=\"closeReplyModal()\" class=\"btn-close\">✕</button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"modal-body\">\n                <input type=\"hidden\" id=\"reply-annotation-id\">\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label>批注内容：</label>\n                    <p id=\"reply-annotation-content\"></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"admin-reply\">管理员回复：</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"admin-reply\" rows=\"4\" placeholder=\"请输入回复内容...\"></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-actions\">\n                    <button onclick=\"closeReplyModal()\" class=\"btn-secondary\">取消</button>\n                    <button onclick=\"submitReply()\" class=\"btn-primary\">提交回复</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <script>\n        const API_BASE = '/abyss/api';\n        let adminToken = '';\n        \n        // 登录\n        document.getElementById('login-form').addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {\n            e.preventDefault();\n            adminToken = document.getElementById('admin-token').value;\n            \n            // 验证token\n            try {\n                const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/admin/stats`, {\n                    headers: { 'X-Admin-Token': adminToken }\n                });\n                \n                const result = await response.json();\n                \n                if (result.success) {\n                    document.getElementById('login-screen').classList.add('hidden');\n                    document.getElementById('admin-screen').classList.remove('hidden');\n                    loadChapterFilter();\n                    loadStats();\n                    loadAnnotations();\n                } else {\n                    alert('登录失败：' + result.error);\n                }\n            } catch (error) {\n                console.error('登录失败:', error);\n                alert('登录失败，请检查网络连接');\n            }\n        });\n        \n        // 加载章节筛选器\n        function loadChapterFilter() {\n            const select = document.getElementById('chapter-filter');\n            for (let i = 1; i <= 45; i++) {\n                const option = document.createElement('option');\n                option.value = i;\n                option.textContent = `第${i}章`;\n                select.appendChild(option);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 加载统计数据\n        async function loadStats() {\n            try {\n                const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/admin/stats`, {\n                    headers: { 'X-Admin-Token': adminToken }\n                });\n                \n                const result = await response.json();\n                \n                if (result.success) {\n                    document.getElementById('total-count').textContent = result.data.total;\n                    document.getElementById('pending-count').textContent = result.data.pending;\n                    document.getElementById('accepted-count').textContent = result.data.accepted;\n                    document.getElementById('rejected-count').textContent = result.data.rejected;\n                }\n            } catch (error) {\n                console.error('加载统计失败:', error);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 加载批注列表\n        async function loadAnnotations() {\n            const status = document.getElementById('status-filter').value;\n            const chapter = document.getElementById('chapter-filter').value;\n            \n            let url = `${API_BASE}/admin/annotations?`;\n            if (status) url += `status=${status}&`;\n            if (chapter) url += `chapter=${chapter}`;\n            \n            try {\n                const response = await fetch(url, {\n                    headers: { 'X-Admin-Token': adminToken }\n                });\n                \n                const result = await response.json();\n                \n                if (result.success) {\n                    displayAnnotations(result.data.annotations);\n                    loadStats(); // 更新统计\n                }\n            } catch (error) {\n                console.error('加载批注失败:', error);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 显示批注列表\n        function displayAnnotations(annotations) {\n            const tbody = document.getElementById('annotation-tbody');\n            \n            if (annotations.length === 0) {\n                tbody.innerHTML = `\n                    <tr>\n                        <td colspan=\"8\" class=\"empty-state\">\n                            暂无批注数据\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                `;\n                return;\n            }\n            \n            tbody.innerHTML = annotations.map(ann => `\n                <tr>\n                    <td>第${ann.chapter}章</td>\n                    <td class=\"paragraph-preview\" title=\"${escapeHtml(ann.paragraph_text)}\">\n                        ${escapeHtml(ann.paragraph_text)}\n                    </td>\n                    <td class=\"annotation-content-preview\">\n                        ${escapeHtml(ann.content)}\n                    </td>\n                    <td>${getTypeName(ann.type)}</td>\n                    <td>${escapeHtml(ann.author)}</td>\n                    <td>\n                        <span class=\"status-badge ${ann.status}\">\n                            ${getStatusName(ann.status)}\n                        </span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td>${formatDate(ann.created_at)}</td>\n                    <td>\n                        <div class=\"action-buttons\">\n                            <button onclick=\"acceptAnnotation('${ann.id}')\" \n                                    class=\"btn-accept\" ${ann.status === 'accepted' ? 'disabled' : ''}>\n                                采纳\n                            </button>\n                            <button onclick=\"rejectAnnotation('${ann.id}')\"\n                                    class=\"btn-reject\" ${ann.status === 'rejected' ? 'disabled' : ''}>\n                                拒绝\n                            </button>\n                            <button onclick=\"openReplyModal('${ann.id}', '${escapeHtml(ann.content)}')\"\n                                    class=\"btn-reply\">\n                                回复\n                            </button>\n                            <button onclick=\"deleteAnnotation('${ann.id}')\"\n                                    class=\"btn-delete\">\n                                删除\n                            </button>\n                        </div>\n                    </td>\n                </tr>\n            `).join('');\n        }\n        \n        // 采纳批注\n        async function acceptAnnotation(id) {\n            if (!confirm('确定要采纳这条批注吗？')) return;\n            \n            try {\n                const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/admin/annotations/${id}`, {\n                    method: 'PATCH',\n                    headers: {\n                        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n                        'X-Admin-Token': adminToken\n                    },\n                    body: JSON.stringify({ status: 'accepted' })\n                });\n                \n                const result = await response.json();\n                \n                if (result.success) {\n                    loadAnnotations();\n                } else {\n                    alert('操作失败：' + result.error);\n                }\n            } catch (error) {\n                console.error('采纳失败:', error);\n                alert('操作失败');\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 拒绝批注\n        async function rejectAnnotation(id) {\n            if (!confirm('确定要拒绝这条批注吗？')) return;\n            \n            try {\n                const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/admin/annotations/${id}`, {\n                    method: 'PATCH',\n                    headers: {\n                        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n                        'X-Admin-Token': adminToken\n                    },\n                    body: JSON.stringify({ status: 'rejected' })\n                });\n                \n                const result = await response.json();\n                \n                if (result.success) {\n                    loadAnnotations();\n                } else {\n                    alert('操作失败：' + result.error);\n                }\n            } catch (error) {\n                console.error('拒绝失败:', error);\n                alert('操作失败');\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 打开回复模态框\n        function openReplyModal(id, content) {\n            document.getElementById('reply-annotation-id').value = id;\n            document.getElementById('reply-annotation-content').textContent = content;\n            document.getElementById('admin-reply').value = '';\n            document.getElementById('reply-modal').classList.remove('hidden');\n        }\n        \n        // 关闭回复模态框\n        function closeReplyModal() {\n            document.getElementById('reply-modal').classList.add('hidden');\n        }\n        \n        // 提交回复\n        async function submitReply() {\n            const id = document.getElementById('reply-annotation-id').value;\n            const reply = document.getElementById('admin-reply').value;\n            \n            if (!reply.trim()) {\n                alert('请输入回复内容');\n                return;\n            }\n            \n            try {\n                const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/admin/annotations/${id}`, {\n                    method: 'PATCH',\n                    headers: {\n                        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n                        'X-Admin-Token': adminToken\n                    },\n                    body: JSON.stringify({\n                        admin_reply: reply,\n                        status: 'accepted',\n                        admin_id: 'admin'\n                    })\n                });\n                \n                const result = await response.json();\n                \n                if (result.success) {\n                    closeReplyModal();\n                    loadAnnotations();\n                } else {\n                    alert('回复失败：' + result.error);\n                }\n            } catch (error) {\n                console.error('回复失败:', error);\n                alert('回复失败');\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 删除批注\n        async function deleteAnnotation(id) {\n            if (!confirm('确定要删除这条批注吗？此操作不可恢复！')) return;\n            \n            try {\n                const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/admin/annotations/${id}`, {\n                    method: 'DELETE',\n                    headers: { 'X-Admin-Token': adminToken }\n                });\n                \n                const result = await response.json();\n                \n                if (result.success) {\n                    loadAnnotations();\n                } else {\n                    alert('删除失败：' + result.error);\n                }\n            } catch (error) {\n                console.error('删除失败:', error);\n                alert('删除失败');\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 辅助函数\n        function escapeHtml(text) {\n            const div = document.createElement('div');\n            div.textContent = text;\n            return div.innerHTML;\n        }\n        \n        function getTypeName(type) {\n            const names = { comment: '💬 评论', correction: '✏️ 纠错', suggestion: '💡 建议' };\n            return names[type] || type;\n        }\n        \n        function getStatusName(status) {\n            const names = { pending: '待处理', accepted: '已采纳', rejected: '已拒绝' };\n            return names[status] || status;\n        }\n        \n        function formatDate(dateStr) {\n            const date = new Date(dateStr);\n            return date.toLocaleDateString('zh-CN') + ' ' + date.toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' });\n        }\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772176594770}}
